steps.name: Given  the user logs in with username "Employee140" and password "Employee123"
And  user navigates to File page
When  user choose Details on the file "Hidden Jem"
And  user click on Comment button
And  user ads comment "Wow, amazing photos, please DM for collaboration!"
Then  user should see comment "Wow, amazing photos, please DM for collaboration!" under the comment section
